data.description: *Multiple offers have been received, please send highest and best offers by 1pm EST on 4/15/24*Welcome to the lovely North Shore area! This home offers modern updates and classic charm in a sought-after location. Situated within walking distance to popular eateries such as Tremont Tavern, Daily Ration, Il Primo, and Southern Squeeze, you'll enjoy easy access to some of Chattanooga's best dining and entertainment options. With an open concept layout, this home boasts beautiful interior features, including fresh paint and updated drywall, windows, plumbing, and electrical systems. Prepare to be wowed by the stunning kitchen featuring luxurious quartz countertops, tiled backsplash, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary needs. The updated flooring throughout offers both durability and elegance, with no carpet in sight. The thoughtful renovations continue with updated retaining walls enhancing the front yard landscaping, an irrigation system ensuring lush greenery year-round, and a brand new hot water heater for efficiency and peace of mind. The spacious one-car garage comes complete with ample storage for all your tools and outdoor gear. Outside, a large back deck awaits, perfect for hosting gatherings around the fire pit under the stars. With two options for off-street parking including a private front driveway and ample space in the back driveway, parking won't be an issue. This home is zoned for award-winning Normal Park Schools. Don't miss your chance to make this incredible property yours - schedule your showing today!
